claim: Emily Blunt is a musical artist.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The musical debuted in San Diego at the Old Globe Theatre in 1986 and premiered on Broadway on November 5 , 1987 , where it won several Tony Awards , including Best Score , Best Book , and Best Actress in a Musical  (  Joanna Gleason  )  , in a year dominated by The Phantom of the Opera  (  1988  )  .
